text: M/S Misana Godby Shipping AB is a Finnish shipping firm, based in Mariehamn in the Åland Islands. It was established in 1973, and as of 2015 its CEO is Dan Mikkola. The shipping company operates seven ro-ro vessels: MS Baltica, MS Mistral, MS Misana, MS Misida, MS Star Link, MS Midas, and MS Mimer. ==References== ==External links== *Official site Category:Shipping companies of Finland Category:Transport companies established in 1973 Category:1973 establishments in Finland Category:Mariehamn Category:Economy of the Åland Islands
